    <!-- main -->

  <main class="section main-section" id="who-we-are">
    <h2 class="bounce-in main-heading">
      About OAE
      <div class="main-heading-underline"></div>
    </h2>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p class="fade-bounce interactive-card">
        <span class="highlight">Oluwatosin Academy of Excellence (OAE)</span> is a forward-thinking educational platform committed to academic brilliance, digital empowerment, and community growth. Founded in 2023 by Mr. Tee, OAE was created with the goal of redefining education in Nigeria, across Africa, and worldwide, by making learning more accessible, engaging, and impactful for students at all levels.
      </p>

      <div class="decorative-quote">
        "Education is not just about passing exams, it's about building futures and empowering minds to shape tomorrow."
      </div>

      <p class="bounce-up interactive-card">
        At OAE, we are deeply passionate about helping students unlock their full potential. Our approach goes beyond traditional classroom learning, combining <span class="emphasis">structured exam preparation</span>, modern digital skills, and engaging educational content to support students in achieving both academic and personal success.
      </p>

      <div class="feature-highlight">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <strong>Expert-Led Learning:</strong> Learn from experienced educators and industry professionals who understand the Nigerian education system.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-highlight">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i></div>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <strong>Innovative Technology:</strong> Cutting-edge digital tools and interactive platforms that make learning fun and effective.
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="bounce-left interactive-card">
        OAE serves as a trusted guide for students preparing for major examinations such as <span class="emphasis">JAMB, WAEC, and NECO</span>. Through carefully curated resources, past questions, practice tools, and explanatory lessons, we help learners build confidence, improve understanding, and perform better in their examinations.
      </p>

      <div class="decorative-divider"></div>

      <div class="mission-statement" id="mission">
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>At Oluwatosin Academy of Excellence (OAE), our mission is to empower learners of all ages to reach their full academic and personal potential. We are dedicated to providing high-quality educational resources, structured guidance, and innovative learning tools that combine traditional academic excellence with modern digital literacy.</p>
        <p>Our approach is student-centered: we strive to make learning engaging, accessible, and effective. From exam preparation for JAMB, WAEC, NECO, and Post-UTME, to foundational coding and technology skills, OAE equips learners with the knowledge and confidence to excel both in school and beyond.</p>
        <p>We also believe in nurturing curiosity, critical thinking, and problem-solving. By blending education with edutainment, motivational content, and community support through OAE CONNECTS, we create an environment where learners are inspired, supported, and motivated to achieve more than they ever thought possible.</p>
        <p>Through this mission, OAE aims to transform the educational landscape in Nigeria, across Africa, and worldwide, preparing students not only to succeed academically but to thrive in a fast-changing, tech-driven world.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="decorative-divider"></div>

      <p class="fade-bounce interactive-card">
        In addition to exam preparation, OAE promotes lifelong learning, personal development, and tech literacy. By integrating technology, coding education, and edutainment into our platform, we prepare students not only for exams, but also for a future shaped by digital innovation.
      </p>

      <div class="feature-highlight">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <strong>Future-Ready Skills:</strong> From coding and digital literacy to entrepreneurship and critical thinking.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-highlight">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i></div>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <strong>Global Perspective:</strong> Connecting Nigerian students with international opportunities and global best practices.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What We Offer Section -->
      <div class="what-we-offer-section" id="careers">
        <h3 class="section-title bounce-in offer-section-title">
          What We Offer
          <div class="offer-title-underline"></div>
        </h3>

        <div class="offer-intro bounce-up">
          <p>
            At OAE, we provide a well-rounded learning experience designed to support students academically, digitally, and mentally. Our offerings are carefully structured to meet the needs of secondary school students, exam candidates, and university learners.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="offerings-grid">
          <!-- Exam Resources -->
          <div class="offering-card slide-in-right" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="offering-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="offering-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">Exam Resources</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
              We provide access to past questions, verified answers, and detailed explanations for all major Nigerian examinations, including JAMB, WAEC, NECO, and Post-UTME. These resources are designed to help students understand exam patterns, improve accuracy, and build confidence through consistent practice.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Subject Tutorials -->
          <div class="offering-card slide-in-right" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="offering-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="offering-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">Subject Tutorials</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
              OAE offers in-depth and easy-to-follow lessons across a wide range of subjects such as Biology, Physics, English Language, Literature-in-English, IRS, Chemistry, Government, and more. Each tutorial is structured to simplify complex topics and align with official exam syllabuses.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Beginner-Friendly Coding -->
          <div class="offering-card slide-in-right" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="offering-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="offering-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">Beginner-Friendly Coding</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
              We introduce learners to coding and digital skills through beginner-friendly tutorials in JavaScript, Python, SQL, and other foundational programming concepts. Our approach focuses on clarity, step-by-step explanations, and practical understanding, making tech accessible even to complete beginners.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Advanced Topics -->
          <div class="offering-card slide-in-right" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="offering-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="offering-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">Advanced Topics</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
              For university students and advanced learners, OAE simplifies higher-level topics such as multi-level statistics and other complex academic concepts. We break these topics down into understandable lessons that support academic success at the tertiary level.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Edutainment & Motivation -->
          <div class="offering-card slide-in-right" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="offering-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="offering-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-tv"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">Edutainment & Motivation</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
              Through OAE MEDIA TV, we combine education with entertainment to keep learning engaging and relatable. Our content includes humor, tech news, motivational clips, and academic inspiration designed to encourage consistency, positivity, and a strong learning mindset.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="decorative-divider"></div>

      <!-- Who We Serve Section -->
      <div class="section-container" id="story" style="margin:4rem 0;">
        <div class="section-title fade-in-up" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
          <h2 style="font-size:2.5rem;color:#212121;margin-bottom:0.5rem;position:relative;display:inline-block;">
            Who We Serve
            <div style="position:absolute;bottom:-10px;left:0;right:0;height:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#28A745,#28A745);border-radius:2px;"></div>
          </h2>
          <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#212121;max-width:800px;margin:1rem auto 0;line-height:1.6;text-align:center;">
            At OAE, we provide a well-rounded learning experience designed to support students academically, digitally, and mentally. Our offerings are carefully structured to meet the needs of secondary school students, exam candidates, and university learners.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="audience-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:2rem;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">

          <!-- Secondary School Students -->
          <div class="audience-card slide-in-left" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="audience-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="audience-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">Secondary School Students</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;text-align:center;">
              We support students preparing for crucial national examinations like JAMB, WAEC, NECO, and GCE. Our comprehensive resources, practice questions, and expert guidance help students build confidence and achieve their academic goals.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- University Students -->
          <div class="audience-card slide-in-right" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="audience-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="audience-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-university"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">University Students</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;text-align:center;">
              University undergraduates benefit from our advanced tutorials covering complex topics in mathematics, statistics, and other specialized subjects. We help students excel in their courses and prepare for professional careers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Tech Beginners -->
          <div class="audience-card slide-in-left" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:2rem;border-radius:15px;margin:1rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,0.1);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(40,167,69,0.08);transition:all 0.3s ease;">
            <div class="audience-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <div class="audience-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28A745,#28A745);color:white;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#212121;margin:0;font-size:1.3rem;">Tech Beginners</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#212121;line-height:1.6;margin:0;text-align:center;">
              Whether you're interested in web development, data analysis, or digital marketing, our beginner-friendly coding tutorials and tech resources make learning programming accessible and enjoyable for complete newcomers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Lifelong Learners -->
